name: Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger: Game de Gaburincho!!
overview: Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger: Game de Gaburincho! ( 獣電戦隊キョウリュウジャー：ゲームでガブリンチョ！！ Juuden Sentai Kyouryuuja: Ge'mu de Gaburincho!!?) is a game developed by SeventhChord and published by Bandai Namco Games for the 3DS in 2013. It is based on the 37th season of the Super Sentai franchise, which was adapted by Saban Brands in 2015 as Power Rangers Dino Charge and Dino Super Charge. Despite the series being popular enough in South Korea to warrant a sequel series collaboration with Daewon Media titled Power Rangers Dino Force Brave, the 3DS game remained Japan-exclusive.
